title: Jewel Mint By Pod Juice 55
description: The most sought after salt nicotine E-Liquid is finally here! It's truly a mint e-liquid masterpiece that is so close to the real "thing", you won't be able to tell the difference! It's the signature fresh and cooling mint that everyone knows and loves. Jewel Mint by Pod Juice is insanely popular with menthol lovers, and will absolutely blow your mind.
